<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Digital-tv-box_fr%C3%A5n_Nokia.jpg" class="image" title="Digital TV set-top box"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f9/Digital-tv-box_fr%C3%A5n_Nokia.jpg/300px-Digital-tv-box_fr%C3%A5n_Nokia.jpg" width="300" height="225" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
